@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_fqxbfi(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.63 * v1 + 0.12)) - 0.32)
    tmp = 0.94
    v0 = tmp
    v2 = wp.abs(v0)
    v1 = 0.63
    v1 = ((v2 + (tmp + 0.78 / tmp + 0.35)) + ((tmp + 0.36 + tmp + 0.94) / tmp))
    tmp = (0.16 - wp.sin((v1 + 0.79 + tmp + 0.42)))
    v0 = (tmp * v0)
    data[tid] = v0
